            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sweet potato & spinach curry</strong> with the <strong>saffron & lemon rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
